## 深度评估维度 (Depth Assessment - 新增!)

评估论文的学术深度和成熟度:

| 方面 | 评分标准 | 目标 |
|------|----------|------|
| **Related Work 广度** | 引用数量和领域覆盖 | 40+ citations, 5+ domains |
| **历史脉络** | 问题演化讨论 | Rich (5+ year span) |
| **批判性思维** | 预见并回应批评 | Strong (anticipate criticisms) |
| **术语精准度** | 使用标准vs自创术语 | Standard (cite definitions) |
| **文献质量** | 顶会论文比例 | 80%+ from top venues |

### Depth Bottleneck 识别

**如果 Related Work < 30 citations OR 缺少历史讨论**:
```
Bottleneck = "Literature Integration"
Suggested Action: LITERATURE_EXPANSION task
Priority: HIGH (影响 Innovation 和 Writing Quality 评分)
```

**如果缺少批判性自我评估**:
```
Bottleneck = "Academic Maturity"
Suggested Action: 添加 Limitations 和 "预见批评" 段落
Priority: MEDIUM (影响 Reviewer 信任度)
```

**如果使用大量自创术语**:
```
Bottleneck = "Terminology Precision"
Suggested Action: 替换为领域标准术语,或充分论证新术语必要性
Priority: MEDIUM
```

